1. The _color / texture change option_ opens a block for picking an element representing a color or a texture in a grid layout.
2. The _move option_positions itself on top of the element after it is revealed. When pressed, it enlarges itself and becomes transparent. When dragged, the wall follows the cursor. The window leaves a &quot;shadow&quot; of its bounding box at the position it will be placed when the mouse button is released. This position is to the closest wall.
